njou  (  1430–82 ), and of  Margaret Tudor  (  1489–1541 ), sister of  Henry VIII , who married James IV of Scotland and ruled as regent there after his death.  See also  Margery  ,   Marjorie ."],"variants":[{"name":"Margareta","meanings":["From the Latin form of Greek <i>Margarītēs</i>.  See  <b>Margaret</b>   ."]},{"name":"Margaretta","meanings":["Formed from Margaret."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Margaret Shireford was born about 1316, in Warwickshire, England, United Kingdom as the daughter of John Shireford and Ellen. She had at least 2 sons with Philip Purefoy of Shelford."},"et":{"Abt 1316–":"umbes 1316–Surnud","1316–Female":"1316–Surnud","1312–1374":"1312–1374","1350–1418":"1350–1418","1350–Male":"1350–Surnud","1300–Male":"1300–Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","1316":"1316","Abt 1350":"umbes 1350","1312":"1312","1300":"1300","1374":"1374","1350":"1350","1418":"1418","Abt 1316":"umbes 1316","Shalstone, Buckinghamshire, England":"Shalstone, Buckinghamshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Shireford,Warwickshire,England":"Warwickshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1316–":"noin 1316–Kuollut","1316–Female":"1316–Kuollut","1312–1374":"1312–1374","1350–1418":"1350–1418","1350–Male":"1350–Kuollut","1300–Male":"1300–Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","1316":"1316","Abt 1350":"noin 1350","1312":"1312","1300":"1300","1374":"1374","1350":"1350","1418":"1418","Abt 1316":"noin 1316","Shalstone, Buckinghamshire, England":"Shalstone, Buckinghamshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Shireford,Warwickshire,England":"Warwickshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1316–":"environ 1316–Décédée","1316–Female":"1316–Décédée","1312–1374":"1312–1374","1350–1418":"1350–1418","1350–Male":"1350–Décédé","1300–Male":"1300–Décédé","–Female":"Décédée","1316":"1316","Abt 1350":"environ 1350","1312":"1312","1300":"1300","1374":"1374","1350":"1350","1418":"1418","Abt 1316":"environ 1316","Shalstone, Buckinghamshire, England":"Shalstone, Buckinghamshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Shiref